title: 'Not efficient'
body: Not able to fit in bigger size papers apart from A1 size. Not much of gap between compartments. It's very compact not friendly. Single file sheet is lot better than this.

title: 'One of the best files you can find but..'
body: This has labels that come with the file but the rope like thing wasn't my fav still one of the best and sturdy file

title: 'Received the same as it looks'
body: 'Product is the same as show and quite good aesthetically. Has multiple compartments with label space Overall a good purchase'
